title: DDFP 119: The Sheky Awards
itunes:title: DDFP 119: The Sheky Awards
description:
Shek and Rank are joined by Handsome Hank and ATL writers Dan Hanzus and Marc Sessler to give away the 2012 Sheky Awards for best fruit, condiment, new guest, land of the fox, movies that Dave enjoys and the coveted Sonic Award. Also, on the "ATL Debate Club," Hanzus and Sessler decide who has the most to lose in this year's playoff derby.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
